Titolo: Game & Watch: Super Mario Bros.

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Game & Watch: Super Mario Bros. was a limited-edition Game & Watch system developed and published by Nintendo, released on November 13, 2020. The system is a compilation of three prior Nintendo games, Super Mario Bros., Super Mario Bros.: The Lost Levels (known as Super Mario Bros. 2 in Japan), and Ball. The system was released to commemorate the 35th anniversary of the Super Mario series, as well as the 40th anniversary of the Game & Watch line of systems.In June 2021, Nintendo announced Game & Watch: The Legend of Zelda, a similar release celebrating the 35th anniversary of The Legend of Zelda, which was released on November 12, 2021. It is a compilation of three games from the Legend of Zelda series, including the NES versions of The Legend of Zelda and Zelda II: The Adventure of Link, and the Game Boy version of The Legend of Zelda: Linkâ€™s Awakening, as well as a new Zelda-themed variant of Vermin.